    "id": "81liz",
    "text_zh": "With the last of its strength, the spell speaks to you. 'I'm supposed to curse you by turning your hands green and webbed. But that seems pretty pointless in your case, so I'm going just going to let you off.' With that, it departs for its home in the nether-world.",
