    "text_zh": "The troll slowly walks over to you and bends down. Then, with a lightning-quick movement he grabs you. He holds you gently in his huge hands, but escape is impossible. You can see nothing, but the background noise of the forest suddenly drops and you seem to be indoors. Then, for a moment, his grip relaxes and you have enough space to leap free.",
