    "text_zh": "The elf studies you for a while, then speaks in a clear, emotionless voice. 'You can do less harm this way.' Without a word, she stands and disappears back into the forest. You feel an overwhelming sense of despair. This form seems a fitting punishment for you, and for a moment you are unsure whether you ever really were human.",
