    "id": "Karraowythcc",
    "text_zh": "The porter of your flophouse idly mentions that some men were asking after you a while back. You ask for a description. To your horror you recognise them - senior retainers of your former lord. You realise he's traced you to Karrakara, and has no intention of letting you go.",
