    "text_zh": "The child takes you to where he dropped the key - one of the many grilles that lead to Karrakara's extensive sewer system. You can't fit your arms through, or dislodge the grille. But in Karrakara there's always an opportunity to wallow in filth, and you soon find a nearby grille which you can both remove and fit through.",
