    "text_zh": "'You know', you say, 'You might be over-thinking this. How many gods are here?'<br><br>'A few thousand' Yag-kosha replies.<br><br>'Do you think a few thousand of you could beat Nara in a fight?'<br><br>The two gods mumble and look at the floor. You hear a few thousand embarrassed coughs.",
