    "text_zh": "Lolz points into the darkness. You walk along the row of silent gods like a prisoner walking to execution. The tunnel starts to climb and twist, snaking up, presumably to the tip of the pyramid. There are no more gods. Instead the tunnel is lined with holes, like the portholes of a ship. Smoke billows from the holes, then is sucked in again, then out...it reminds you of breath on a cold day.",
