    "id": "Weighquesty2",
    "text_zh": "You ask around about the worshippers of Nara. It's fairly easy to find out that their predatory priests move from city to city, but that the cult maintains its base in its high temple - a weed-covered pyramid somewhere over the hills. As soon as you can get fair directions, you gather your belongings and set out.",
