    "text_zh": "You find your way blocked by a river. It occurs to you that it could lead to Karrakara, as all currents are said to do. It's also wide enough to be the great Swanroad, the legendary river that flows both from and to the underworld. On the near bank is a boat. A woman, apparently dead, lies in state in the stern. A man has stopped rowing, in the grip of extreme fatigue or despair.",
