    "id": "371a",
    "text_zh": "When the voices offer you twenty shells to be paid when you return, you accept instantly, unable to bargain or even consider whether the price is worth it. The old woman hands you a small package wrapped in oily cloth and bound with leather cords. She repeats the instructions on how to find your destination - some way into the forest that begins an hour's journey from town.",
