    "text_zh": "As you get closer you see a city, all made of stone. In front of the city there stands a giant, hideous creature, with a tentacled head and huge, bat-like wings, all covered in the slime of the sea. Staring at its crab-like claws, you feel as helpless as an ant before a lion.",
