    "id": "chainexplorehelp1",
    "text_zh": "She thanks you, but refuses to let you take watch alone. She describes the awful forms that her fellow exiles have taken. You seem to see the horrors she describes in front of you. Finally, you do indeed see one such monster. She screams a warcry, and you raise your WEAPONNAME.",
